               <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "heatmap"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/paper-anatomy/vocab#histogramFigure
:histogramFigure rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                          <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> ;
                 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> :FigureTypeScheme ;
